00:17:21,633 --> 00:17:24,918
un zey hobn avekgeshtelt di vegns mit di zakhn

281
00:17:25,379 --> 00:17:27,326
un di ferd hobn zey genumen

282
00:17:27,337 --> 00:17:31,246
un undz hobn zey avekgefirt in Vilkomir in di kazarmes.

