00:17:43,706 --> 00:17:47,059
hobn zey genumen, zey hobn getribn ale mener oyfn hoyf

288
00:17:47,942 --> 00:17:53,826
un zey hobn genumen zikh funanderklaybn ver s'iz a komunist un ver s'iz nit keyn komunist

