00:18:15,082 --> 00:18:16,708
in shtot farvaltung

295
00:18:16,832 --> 00:18:17,957
Bramson.

296
00:18:19,397 --> 00:18:21,281
hot men im aroysgenumen.

297
00:18:21,557 --> 00:18:23,006
m'hot aroysgenumen eynem

298
00:18:23,006 --> 00:18:24,735
Yankele Shvarts.

