00:18:27,699 --> 00:18:28,689
on hor.

301
00:18:29,724 --> 00:18:32,520
un azoy hot men genumen nokh mentshn

302
00:18:32,930 --> 00:18:37,244
ober bay nakht hot zikh gefunen eyne vos zi

