00:18:44,608 --> 00:18:48,045
 vo- vos zi iz avek tsu di daytshn

308
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:54,659
un zi hot ge- nit ⟨vayle zi hot⟩ gekent reydn, un zi hot ⟨erleydikt⟩, m'hot alemen opgelozt.

309
00:18:54,699 --> 00:18:55,757
a yidishe?

310
00:18:55,577 --> 00:18:56,533
a yidishe.

311
00:18:56,117 --> 00:18:57,816
vos zi hot gekent redn daytsh.

