00:18:57,973 --> 00:19:02,676
zi hot nit gekent reydn keyn daytsh. UNK ⟨tsuzamen⟩ geredt, umetum geven ⟨PEREVOZ⟩.

313
00:19:03,575 --> 00:19:07,079
s'past oder tsu z- zi hot gekent arayngeyn in bet.

