00:19:08,688 --> 00:19:11,889
nor s'iz do do azelkhe oykhet. a gute, zi hot geholfn.

315
00:19:11,253 --> 00:19:11,757
ye.

316
00:19:11,757 --> 00:19:14,032
un me, m'hot, m'hot bafrayt zey alemen.

317
00:19:14,308 --> 00:19:18,186
s'iz geven a fal az mir zaynen ge- baym ⟨krogn⟩ shpeter

318
00:19:18,206 --> 00:19:19,770
nokh etlekhe teg

319
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:22,875
oyf daytsh heyst dos SCHEINEN

320
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:25,982
az mir megn zikh kenen kerik

321
00:19:25,982 --> 00:19:27,633
bay undz in di shtiber.

322
00:19:28,213 --> 00:19:29,777
zaynen mir geforn

