zeyer familye iz geven Zayontshik.

356
00:21:31,653 --> 00:21:33,284
hobn gehat tsvey meydlekh

357
00:21:33,408 --> 00:21:34,263
kleyne.

358
00:21:38,538 --> 00:21:40,220
un dortn bin ikh arayn.

359
