362
00:21:52,005 --> 00:21:53,974
ober ikh hob gehert in shtub

363
00:21:54,401 --> 00:21:55,875
az baym brik

364
00:21:55,875 --> 00:21:57,163
khapt men yidn.

365
00:21:58,755 --> 00:22:04,082
ikh bin tsu bizn kiosk. keyner hot mir nit getshepet, ober der kiosk iz geven farmakht

366
00:22:04,155 --> 00:22:09,128
hob ikh zikh umgekert biz KRISCIUKAICIO gas, ver es ken Slabodke, fun brik

367
00:22:09,352 --> 00:22:15,331
un ikh hob ⟨zikh⟩ avekgeshtelt fun hintn un ikh hob gekukt tsi me khapt vemen. dervayle hot men mir ongenumen farn kolner

368
00:22:15,331 --> 00:22:20,146
un m'hot mir arayngefirt lebn brik, iz geven a ⟨rimer⟩, ver s'iz a Kovner veyst vu dos iz

369
00:22:20,642 --> 00:22:24,973
un in ovnt hot men undz avekgefirt oyfn zibetn fort.

370
00:22:26,345 --> 00:22:27,183
mir.

371
00:22:29,501 --> 00:22:32,131
dortn hot men undz arayngetribn

372
00:22:32,131 --> 00:22:37,680
un m'hot gegebn fun flonderke, fun gezaltsene fish, di beyner oysgekokht a bisl vaser

373
00:22:38,681 --> 00:22:40,228
un m'hot ongezogt

374
00:22:40,571 --> 00:22:45,054
az ver es vet zikh bay nakht gebn a drey vet vern dershosn.

375
