un arayngefirt in Slabodke durkh Linkever gas.

406
00:24:42,594 --> 00:24:44,363
hot men undz aroysgefirt

407
00:24:44,363 --> 00:24:45,224
tsu

408
00:24:45,224 --> 00:24:46,439
PANERIU

409
00:24:46,439 --> 00:24:48,591
un aroyfgefirt dem barg

410
00:24:48,602 --> 00:24:51,617
oyf, vos es geyt oyf KLAIPEDA.

411
00:24:53,343 --> 00:24:56,527
dortn hot men undz avekgefirt oyfn nayntn fort.

412
00:24:58,322 --> 00:25:03,868
