00:25:24,647 --> 00:25:30,969
eyn tog iz gevorn a trevoge. m'hot ⟨zey gehat⟩ tsugenumen di gantse vakh, un m'hot ibergelozn dortn eynem

419
00:25:35,548 --> 00:25:41,182
un ikh fleg aroystrogn di mist, flegt mit mir mitgeyn nokh a, a postn.

420
00:25:41,182 --> 00:25:42,394
ah

421
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:44,160
un

422
00:25:44,171 --> 00:25:47,405
zeen vi ikh shit oys di mist un mir mitnemen kerik

423
00:25:47,799 --> 00:25:51,371
az s'iz keyner nit geven, hob ikh gefregt bay dem UNK

424
00:25:51,444 --> 00:25:53,818
vos zol ikh ton haynt mit di mist?

425
00:25:54,026 --> 00:25:57,665
zogt er "gey aleyn avek un shit oys di mist, vest kumen kerik."

426
00:25:58,262 --> 00:26:00,973
un dos iz geven velkhe nit iz

427
00:26:01,046 --> 00:26:06,440
nit merer vi hundert meter tsum k- tsum veg, tsu di tsentrale veg.

428
00:26:07,509 --> 00:26:09,371
bay di tsentrale veg

429
00:26:09,416 --> 00:26:13,173
hobn di daytshn oysgeleygt shtroy un aroyfgegosn kalkh.

430
00:26:13,432 --> 00:26:16,379
s'iz gegangen epes a epidemye fun beheymes

431
00:26:16,571 --> 00:26:24,145
az m'hot zikh gedarft opvishn di fis, un di mashines hobn gedarft ale zikh opshteln un aruntergeyn, tsi soldatn tsi nit keyn soldatn

432
00:26:24,145 --> 00:26:25,914
un opvishn di fis.

433
00:26:26,612 --> 00:26:28,193
in der tsayt

434
00:26:28,856 --> 00:26:32,765
di soldatn zaynen aroyf, hob ikh zikh arayngekhapt bay zey in mashin

435
00:26:33,092 --> 00:26:35,584
vayl ikh hob farshtanen az me vet mir bald zukhn

436
00:26:36,163 --> 00:26:39,246
un ikh bin aruntergeforn fun barg

437
00:26:40,230 --> 00:26:46,924
oyf PANERIU gas. hob ikh aroysgetantst fun di mashin, dortn ⟨hob ikh⟩ zikh gemuzt ⟨falt⟩ vayle me darf zikh fardreyen

438
00:26:47,756 --> 00:26:52,779
un ikh hob aroysgetantst fun di mashin un UNK arayngegangen in a shtub

439
00:26:53,865 --> 00:26:58,905
vos zey hobn mir gekent, un ikh hob dortn nokhgekhapt a bulve, zey hobn gegesn bulves mit hering

440
00:26:59,147 --> 00:27:07,984
un ikh bin glaykh avekgelofn oyf PANERIU draytsn. ven ikh bin gekumen oyf PANERIU draytsn bay di tantn, hob ikh gefunen az der pape mit di mamen zitsn shoyn nokh mir shive

441
00:27:08,158 --> 00:27:11,831
un oyf di shvester vos iz dershtikt gevorn in Yanever keler

442
00:27:13,457 --> 00:27:15,088
zitsn zey shive

443
00:27:15,279 --> 00:27:19,543
"sha! shrayt nit!" altsding, ikh hob zey dertseylt vi s'iz geven un altskeding

444
00:27:20,848 --> 00:27:25,972
un azoy zaynen mir shoyn geven biz mir zaynen, biz m'hot farmakht di geto.

445
00:27:26,433 --> 00:27:28,773
yetst volt ikh aykh nokh gevolt fregn a frage.

446
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:33,228
zayendik in dem zibetn un dem nayntn fort, azoy vi dertseylt frier

447
00:27:33,302 --> 00:27:38,230
ver hot oyf, ver hot ge-, ver iz geven di vakht, un ver hot geven di shisers? s'iz geven alts litviner?

448
00:27:37,993 --> 00:27:39,388
alts litviner.

449
00:27:39,714 --> 00:27:45,902
un dos iz geven ven? s'iz geven a kurtse tsayt nokh dem vi di daytshn hobn okupirt ⟨itst⟩ in eyn un fertsik, zumer eyn un fertsik?

450
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:49,310
 di daytshn zaynen geven arayn, dos iz geven mistome in

451
00:27:49,788 --> 00:27:51,824
efsher a, biz a vokh.

452
00:27:52,016 --> 00:27:56,094
an- a vokh nokh dem vi di daytshn zenen arayn? heyst dos zumer eyn un fertsik?

453
00:27:55,644 --> 00:27:56,499
ye.

454
00:27:57,045 --> 00:27:59,672
yetst zent ir shoyn tsuzamen mit di eltern.

455
00:27:59,897 --> 00:28:01,987
un s'iz aroysgegangen a bafel

456
00:28:01,987 --> 00:28:03,637
az biz dem tog

457
00:28:04,993 --> 00:28:06,439
biz dem tog

458
00:28:07,305 --> 00:28:14,961
darfn ale arayngeyn in di, in di dires, di yidishe politsey, m'hot geshafn a yidishe politsey

459
00:28:15,236 --> 00:28:17,587
un m'hot genumen teyln

460
00:28:17,587 --> 00:28:18,994
dires

461
00:28:19,067 --> 00:28:19,967
dortn.

462
00:28:19,978 --> 00:28:23,398
hot men gegebn afile in eyn tsimer tsvey mishpokhes.

463
00:28:24,348 --> 00:28:29,354
bay undz iz geven, di dire vos mir hobn gekrogn, oyf MOKYKLU zibetsn

464
00:28:31,858 --> 00:28:35,278
hobn mir gekrogn di dire mit nokh

465
00:28:36,785 --> 00:28:38,787
tsvey froyen mit a kind.

466
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:45,824
iz flegt men ibertsoymen dem tsimer mit a paravan, a mol hot zikh geheysn dos

467
00:28:45,948 --> 00:28:49,182
un mir hobn gelebt in dem halbn un zey in dem halbn.

468
00:28:49,644 --> 00:28:52,282
un nokh dem hot zikh ongehoybn az me darf geyn

469
00:28:52,282 --> 00:28:53,486
arbetn

470
00:28:55,230 --> 00:28:58,447
tsu der arbet. flegt men arbetn oyfn erodrom.

471
00:28:58,740 --> 00:29:04,388
me flegt arbetn, in farshidene erter vu di daytshn hobn gedarft.

472
00:29:04,022 --> 00:29:06,177
vos heyst "me fleg-" ir, vos hot ir gemakht?

473
00:29:07,042 --> 00:29:10,698
ikh als kind, hot men mir tsu der arbet nit gekhapt.

474
00:29:10,957 --> 00:29:15,002
ober ikh hob aleyn gezukht arbet kedey tsu khapn a shtikl broyt.

